\pard\plain \ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 I don\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92t think I ever felt certain of him. Except on my wedding day I did feel a sense of \u8220\'93peace\u8221\'94 and I am not sure if there was a conscious deliberation to manifesting that, but I took it as a sign to go in. But I think I hoped for certaintiy, even though there were a lot of uncertain feelings. Now, since this is my past lived experience, I know I wold never do that again with someone. It\u8217\'92s essentially going into a relationship expecting someone will change.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 I will say too that in the beginning the highs wer HIGH and the lows wer medium low and then it sorta switched entirely}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Promises were made, compliments were showered etc. etc.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 I don\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92t think I have an entire definition of love locked in, but part of it is safety. Safety to be who you are, your worst and best, with someone else, and regardless, they will remain with you, and in order to remain, they don\u8217\'92t feel like they have to sacrifice any of their genuine selves because of it. Each person, comfortable in their own skin, around the other person.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Alright}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 It\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s very difficult to organize my thoughts here.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 There\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s a lot of things and I\u8217\'92m not quite sure how they fit together yet, but there are two big things that fit together in an obvious way:  I feel very strong feelings for you, and I feel very uncertain about why I feel the things that I do. }
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 I\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92ve previously talked about that uncertainty, where it comes from. In the past I was pretty sure about a bunch of things, one of them being you, others being things like religion, family, etc., and time and time again it turned out that I read these situations completely incorrectly.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Another puzzle piece: sex is much more powerful than I expected. At least, for me it is. It\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s that way for most, I suspect. For you, too? In the course of trying to understand how you could have fallen for the ex, I began to suspect that one of those factors was sex. You two had sex, I assume you had a lot of sex, given your high sex drive, and this must have played a role in bonding you to him despite any apparent red flags. I\u8217\'92m kind of reading in between the lines here, but I don\u8217\'92t think I\u8217\'92m reading that deep because, you know, you did think of him in the middle of me. Also, in the past you\u8217\'92ve mentioned struggling with resurfaced memories of the HIGH highs you had with him\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 I doubt those highs were riding off the back of his wit. #uncertainty}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 And then this makes me think that maybe we moved too fast. I do thoroughly enjoy having sex with you. I\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92m just thinking out loud, trying to understand what is shaping my attachment to you, and you to me. There are a whole lot of things that I like about you, and one of the big things I like is how you feel about me, but I hesitate there because I\u8217\'92m concerned I might be inventing that, like I\u8217\'92ve done in the past. Concerned as well that sex might be doing the heavy lifting, as it seems sex really floods the body with those hormones.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 To be clear, I do feel affection coming from you. It\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s just that the assymetry of our respective pasts is quite large, and as you intimated last night, probably even bigger than either of us might suspect.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 There are other things, too, but my thumbs are losing their will to live. Suffice to say, this is complex, but also simple, like you said. Really trying to lean into the simple, but my brain likes to latch onto the complex. I think the main takeaway from this fhdm is: I like you a lot, and it spooks me. I think I\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92ve expressed that before, and I\u8217\'92ll repeat what I said then\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 I\u8217\'92m not going to let this anxious fear get in the way of how happy you make me feel.  I just reeeeeally wish that anxious fear wasn\u8217\'92t there so I didn\u8217\'92t have to deal with it. It\u8217\'92s kind of like dog hair.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1
